Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:45.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}私たちまた　現世に交わる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:52.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}そのキレイな眸を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:56.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}覗き込めば　甦えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:59.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}繭のなか　寄り添って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:03.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}夢を喰んだ日々
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:07.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}あるいは絡めた指
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:10.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}互いの血に　塗れ甘く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:14.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}流れる時の川へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:18.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}散ったことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.99,0:23:22.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}絹帯と鎖で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:29.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}双つの運命は結ばれ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}生きて出逢い　惹かれ合ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:36.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}それが何より　強い武器だわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:40.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}闇も悪も　恐れはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:44.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}二人だけでも　いまを戦う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:52.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}美しい救世主になれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:34.16,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}懷抱在胸中的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:37.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}縈繞身體的緋紅記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:41.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}是淚水與笑顏的愛恨交加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:45.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}我們在現世相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:52.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}透過你那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:56.22,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}美麗的眼眸 一切就此復甦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:59.93,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}倚偎在繭中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:03.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}過著以夢為生的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:07.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}又或是手指纏繞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:10.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}被彼此的血抹紅變得鮮甜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:14.57,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}向著時光之河流逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:18.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}分散的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.99,0:23:22.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}用絹帶緊緊連繫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:29.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}兩人的命運就此交織
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.34,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}重生之後的重逢 互相被吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:36.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}這是無可匹敵的 至強武器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:40.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}無論黑暗還是邪惡 無所畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:44.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}只要是你我二人 現在也能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:52.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5\fad(100,100)}成為悅目的救世主
Comment: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,OP(?)-FIRST
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不論陷入何種艱苦戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不論面對怎樣的強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會取得勝利 然後回到你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了的話 就給你一個Kiss！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我…想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧！「沙拉迪加」！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你們快停…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是神足通？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,連我都是花了兩年才學會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個剛剛才覺醒通力的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來救護下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,諸葉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我…剛剛…做了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,諸葉 諸葉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,諸葉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,太古之龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\pos(934.5,975)}Ancient dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:04.67,BackGround,,0,0,0,,諸葉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,太古之龍 又或者叫最古老的英靈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.69,0:24:08.42,BackGround,,0,0,0,,諸葉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,從萬里姐姐口中聽到這個詞時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:11.59,BackGround,,0,0,0,,諸葉 諸葉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.17,0:24:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到了一陣不可思議的脈動…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,話說哥哥說我的胸部很硬是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.93,0:24:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是肋骨啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下一集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.56,0:24:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,寄宿與吾之劍的魔焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,重現我們波瀾的前世！
